<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455633' id='t-455633'>At least if we get beyond a barter economy,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459117' id='t-459117'>somebody has to earn an income</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='461354' id='t-461354'>and someone else has to convert that income</span>
