<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='468092' id='t-468092'>Now most of you, when you hear me</span>
