<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590442' id='t-590442'>The governments that get it --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592778' id='t-592778'>no surprises here --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594625' id='t-594625'>the governments that get it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596465' id='t-596465'>Norway, Sweden, Denmark, the Netherlands,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='601170' id='t-601170'>provide universal child care,</span>
