<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807362' id='t-807362'>I can almost hear lots of you thinking, &quot;No way.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813674' id='t-813674'>But in fact, the change is 
actually already happening.</span>
