<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='924422' id='t-924422'>Thirty years ago, Carol Gilligan,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='926490' id='t-926490'>a wonderful psychologist, studied adolescent girls</span>
