<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937646' id='t-937646'>It turns out that &quot;you don't care&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='940951' id='t-940951'>is just as much a part of who we are</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='943872' id='t-943872'>as &quot;that's not fair.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='946152' id='t-946152'>Bill Gates agrees.</span>
