<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='963363' id='t-963363'>As whole human beings,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='965107' id='t-965107'>we will be better caregivers and breadwinners.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='968951' id='t-968951'>You may think that can't happen,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='971059' id='t-971059'>but I grew up in a society</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='972759' id='t-972759'>where my mother put out small vases</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='975105' id='t-975105'>of cigarettes for dinner parties,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='977767' id='t-977767'>where blacks and whites used separate bathrooms,</span>
